  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Collect and Grow Mushrooms</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fungiculture is a relaxing mushroom farming idle game, designed to thrive in the background as you go about your day. Grow and collect a wide variety of mushrooms, including rare species and even rarer shiny variants, with just the right amount of active involvement.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163580/extras/708516d4e4a8c3c9ee713c86f5237428.poster.avif?t=1729907221\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163580/extras/708516d4e4a8c3c9ee713c86f5237428.webm?t=1729907221\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163580/extras/708516d4e4a8c3c9ee713c86f5237428.mp4?t=1729907221\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Do Some Watering</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Equipped with a simple sprayer, go hands on and create much higher quality yields faster, or just buy some packs and nature take its course, and reap the rewards of your crops to buy even more mushrooms!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163580/extras/9b448b32bfd0d16184ce308d2f610956.poster.avif?t=1729907221\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163580/extras/9b448b32bfd0d16184ce308d2f610956.webm?t=1729907221\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163580/extras/9b448b32bfd0d16184ce308d2f610956.mp4?t=1729907221\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Active Gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as a fairy and guide mushroom spores into your mushrooms to help them grow!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163580/extras/2f431e6286ca5c82baeeba822b68f3c4.poster.avif?t=1729907221\" width=800 height=444 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163580/extras/2f431e6286ca5c82baeeba822b68f3c4.webm?t=1729907221\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163580/extras/2f431e6286ca5c82baeeba822b68f3c4.mp4?t=1729907221\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can also upgrade and customize your fruiting chambers to increase maximum mushrooms, and purchase a new room when you're ready to expand.  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect 77 real-life mushrooms and their rare shinies for a total of 154.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play hands on with your sprayer to increase grow speed and quality, or just let them grow in the background.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sell your mushrooms once mature to earn a profit and buy more.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as a fairy and guide spores into mushrooms to actively help them grow.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade various elements to the game to increase productivity.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade the log size and count in your fruiting chambers to increase the maximum mushroom capacity.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize the background and log designs of your fruiting chambers.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Purchase new fruit chamber for even more mushrooms.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Toggle between upscaled and pixel graphics.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Collect and Grow Mushrooms</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fungiculture is a relaxing mushroom farming idle game, designed to thrive in the background as you go about your day. Grow and collect a wide variety of mushrooms, including rare species and even rarer shiny variants, with just the right amount of active involvement.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163580/extras/708516d4e4a8c3c9ee713c86f5237428.poster.avif?t=1729907221\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163580/extras/708516d4e4a8c3c9ee713c86f5237428.webm?t=1729907221\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163580/extras/708516d4e4a8c3c9ee713c86f5237428.mp4?t=1729907221\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Do Some Watering</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Equipped with a simple sprayer, go hands on and create much higher quality yields faster, or just buy some packs and nature take its course, and reap the rewards of your crops to buy even more mushrooms!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163580/extras/9b448b32bfd0d16184ce308d2f610956.poster.avif?t=1729907221\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163580/extras/9b448b32bfd0d16184ce308d2f610956.webm?t=1729907221\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163580/extras/9b448b32bfd0d16184ce308d2f610956.mp4?t=1729907221\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Active Gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as a fairy and guide mushroom spores into your mushrooms to help them grow!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163580/extras/2f431e6286ca5c82baeeba822b68f3c4.poster.avif?t=1729907221\" width=800 height=444 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163580/extras/2f431e6286ca5c82baeeba822b68f3c4.webm?t=1729907221\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163580/extras/2f431e6286ca5c82baeeba822b68f3c4.mp4?t=1729907221\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can also upgrade and customize your fruiting chambers to increase maximum mushrooms, and purchase a new room when you're ready to expand.  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect 77 real-life mushrooms and their rare shinies for a total of 154.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play hands on with your sprayer to increase grow speed and quality, or just let them grow in the background.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sell your mushrooms once mature to earn a profit and buy more.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as a fairy and guide spores into mushrooms to actively help them grow.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade various elements to the game to increase productivity.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade the log size and count in your fruiting chambers to increase the maximum mushroom capacity.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize the background and log designs of your fruiting chambers.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Purchase new fruit chamber for even more mushrooms.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Toggle between upscaled and pixel graphics.</p></li></ul>",
